### Backend API Test File
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ===== VIDEO ENDPOINTS =====

### Search Videos
GET {{baseUrl}}/video/search?query=music&limit=5

### Get Trending Videos
GET {{baseUrl}}/video/trending?limit=10

### Get Video Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/video/info?url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ

### Get Playlist Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/video/playlist?url=https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLrAXtmErZgOeiKm4sgNOknGvNjby9efdf

### ===== DOWNLOAD ENDPOINTS =====

### Start Single Download (Video)
POST {{baseUrl}}/download
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ",
  "type": "video",
  "quality": "best"
}

### Start Single Download (Audio)
POST {{baseUrl}}/download
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ",
  "type": "audio",
  "quality": "best"
}

### Get Active Downloads
GET {{baseUrl}}/download/active

### Get Download History
GET {{baseUrl}}/download/history

### Cancel Download (replace with actual downloadId)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/download/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

### ===== BATCH DOWNLOAD ENDPOINTS =====

### Start Batch Download
POST {{baseUrl}}/batch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "urls": [
    "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ",
    "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9bZkp7q19f0"
  ],
  "type": "video",
  "quality": "best"
}

### Get All Batches
GET {{baseUrl}}/batch

### Get Batch Status (replace with actual batchId)
GET {{baseUrl}}/batch/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

### Cancel Batch (replace with actual batchId)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/batch/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

### ===== FILE MANAGEMENT ENDPOINTS =====

### List Downloaded Files
GET {{baseUrl}}/files

### Get Download Path
GET {{baseUrl}}/files/path

### Update Download Path
POST {{baseUrl}}/files/path
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "downloadPath": "C:\\Users\\YourUsername\\Downloads\\YT-Downloads"
}

### Delete File (replace with actual filename)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/files/video-title.mp4

### ===== ERROR TESTING =====

### Invalid URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/video/info?url=invalid-url

### Missing Required Field
POST {{baseUrl}}/download
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ"
}

### Empty Search Query
GET {{baseUrl}}/video/search?query=

### Invalid Download Type
POST {{baseUrl}}/download
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ",
  "type": "invalid",
  "quality": "best"
}
